history.content:
This is a moderate to heavy workload schedule, with weekly problem sets for both 170 and 140, and weekly coding HWs for 100.

170 is a challenging class and will take most of your time.

140 is known to be challenging as well (it is definitely harder than Stat 134, known to be a difficult class), depending on your exposure/maturity in probability concepts.

100 is a light to moderate workload class, perhaps comparable to 61A.
